      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/goldman-markets-new-bonds-after-perpetual-notes-deal-this-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团在发行永续票据两天后，就以投资级债券进入市场，该银行在其第一季度业绩出奇强劲后吸引了投资者。]]></description>
